             was indicted for that he, having in his custody a certain bill of exchange, wherein was contained a certain false, forged, and counterfeited acceptance, in writing, with the name Joseph Chaplin Hankey, for Thomas Hankey, Stephen Hall, and himself, and which said bill was in the words and figures following, that is to say,</p>
