                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900707-11-off51 t17900707-11-cd52"></join>, with force and arms feloniously did utter and publish as true, the said false, forged, and counterfeited acceptance, with intention to defraud 
                     
                        <persName id="t17900707-11-victim133" type="victimName">
